show.title: Yes Mr. CEO, We Have A Baby
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/Cy7SHC
show.description: Her life as a respected business scion ended abruptly with an accidental pregnancy, leading to her family's swift disownment and public disgrace. Vanished for six years, she was presumed broken, forgotten. But she returns, not as a victim, but as a silent force of nature. Forged by hardship, she now eyes the very step-sister who built an empire on her ruin. This is a high-stakes saga of betrayal, resilience, and a calculated quest for vengeance set to reshape the powerful world she once lost.
